{"tid":1350694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌達哥不如屌陳怡  大家快啲去report+負皮","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T14:37:27.000Z","uid":13786,"like":178,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b722801eded396567160ecdafd377f17f162cc8a","tid":1350694,"uid":13786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:30:16.000Z","msg":"佢唔為公義發聲不單至<br />\n係反佔中後為左賺大陸人錢仲變身藍絲 <br />\n明明以前出勁多笑大陸人既片<br />\n條條片都係講埋啲歪理 陰謀論<br />\n差唔多每日出一條片 都係剪頭剪尾去抹黑示威者<br />\n今日果條片我睇個topic已經忍唔住心中既憤怒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好屌我成日係到提佢</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而家既情況大家唔可以唔理佢 因為佢已經變左藍絲KOL </strong></span><br />\n洗哂啲藍絲腦 好恐怖<br />\n放任佢只會比啲藍絲share出去洗更多人既腦<br />\n希望大家瘋狂report<br />\nreport到佢啲片比youtube del<br />\n或者冇錢賺<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCO4mttl54gQ0UW-DqyVrvLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCO4mttl54gQ0UW-DqyVrvLQ&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=79ff9614\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCO4mttl54gQ0UW-DqyVrvLQ</a>"},{"pid":"95215422bcec7e244ce257c14ac1a8728deb5a71","tid":1350694,"uid":13786,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪理達狗啦<br />\n集中火力搞死陳怡"},{"pid":"fdc808c0d7cc8832d3f24bc6e6031e0511f850da","tid":1350694,"uid":13786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df5cb06aaf5dee7e5717a61652e668b66509c37","tid":1350694,"uid":13786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaf949a9abac38b373fc75cc7e08cedb77b19ee","tid":1350694,"uid":34377,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:36:29.000Z"